'''Ugboat''' was a localized company on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]]. The corporation's [[Ugboat Building|headquarters]], manufacturing center, and sales floor were located in the city of [[Ugnorgrad/Legends|Ugnorgrad]] on the [[Ugnaught Surface/Legends|Ugnaught Surface]]. They specialized in the creation of [[floatboat]]s for the [[Ugnaught/Legends|Ugnaught]] people and were the largest manufacturer on the Surface of this preferred method of transportation.<ref name="ActionTidings2">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20041007bespin2|series=Bespin: Action Tidings|text=Part 2: That Den o' Human Iniquity}}</ref>

During the rise of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], [[Ars Fivvle]] reported that [[King/Legends|King]] [[Ozz (Ugnaught)/Legends|Ozz]] had secretly acquired ownership of the company and issued a decree that all Ugnaught blood-feuds needed to be resolved on the Ugnaught Surface, thereby increasing demand for transportation and sales of the company's floatboats. Ozz's spokesman, however, denied the accusation.<ref name="ActionTidings2" />

